(OOC: Thanks Soulstice!! *_*)

Teltoli, after just standing on the right side of Windlord, saw 
another bot land on the left side - Aerotaur. She smiled briefly at 
both of them, and waited for the Alliance bot to make a move. 

As Angel Prime landed and started fighting Dark Angel, she cheered 
and suddenly 'eeped', dodging a fireball. The back of her knees hit 
the pod and she tumbled over, landing in a sitting position. She 
smiled up at Aerotaur when he asked, and answered "I'm fine, just a 
little surprised at all of the company!"

The huge shadow of Windlord fell over her, and still sitting in the 
dust, she looked up. After his comment of 'we have to save the lady', 
she got a look on her face, and started to answer when she suddenly 
jumped up as Angel Prime was blasted in front of them.

"Oh gosh, are you alright, sir?" She asked, and quickly checked that 
he was regaining energy. She snarled and turned towards Dark Angel, 
drawing her rapiers and tackling him to the ground with a quick dash 
and a leap. Sitting on top of his chest, she hit him with the full 
strength she could with her blades.
